<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10539" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW">Match Fields</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1053D" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Match the logical field names of the layout dialog to the field names in your database, for new <link href="text/swriter/01/mailmerge03.xhp">address blocks</link> or <link href="text/swriter/01/mailmerge04.xhp">greeting lines</link>.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1054E" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Matches to:</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10552" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">For each logical field element, select a field name from your database.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10555" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Preview</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10559" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">The previews show the values of the first data record.</paragraph>
</body>
